tcome codes evidenced in the supplied official-style model paper. Reconstructed titles are clearly identified as handbook organization, not claimed as official syllabus titles.</p>
    <div class="module-strip">
      <div><b>Module 1</b>Number systems, gates, Boolean algebra, K-Maps</div>
      <div><b>Module 2</b>Logic families and combinational circuits</div>
